==Description==
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
The [[Image:Sketcher_Offset.svg|24px]] [[Sketcher_Offset|Sketcher Offset]] tool creates equidistant edges around selected edges.
</div>

